pydantic>=2.7
pydantic-settings>=2.2
pyyaml>=6.0
structlog>=24.1
python-dotenv>=1.0

---

## CODING STANDARDS

- Python 3.12, full type hints throughout
- Async everywhere (no sync blocking calls)
- Pydantic v2 models only
- All errors caught and re-raised as typed exceptions from core/exceptions.py
- No hardcoded URLs, tokens, or timeouts anywhere — all from config
- Each module has a module-level logger: `log = get_logger(__name__)`
- Include docstrings on all public classes and methods
- Add a README.md covering: local dev setup, adding a new endpoint in 3 steps, 
  env vars reference, K8s deployment steps

---

## DELIVERABLES

Generate ALL files listed in the directory structure above with full working code.
Start with: settings.py → logger.py → connection_manager.py → base_client.py → 
endpoint_registry.py → then the rest in dependency order.
